# Auth
POST `api.axow.se/site/auth` (Credential)
```Headers (Request)
Content-Type: application/json
```
```json (Request)
{
    "username": "<string>",
    "password": "<string:hash>"
}
```
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "token_type": "single",
    "expires": <epoch>,
    "token": "<string:token>"
}
```
<br><br>

# Articles
## Get al the articles
GET `api.axow.se/site/articles?group_filter=<string:optional>&cat_filter=<string:optional>`
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "articles": [
        {
            "id": "<string:article_id>",
            "name": "<string>",
            "author": "<string:profile_id_with_@>",
            "author_title": "<string:comma_list>"
            "published": <epoch>,
            "last_changed": <epoch>,
            "tags": ["<string>"],
            "group": "<string:group>",
            "category": "<string:category>",
            "card_background": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>",
            "favicon": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>",
            "banner": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>"
        }
        ...
    ]
}
```
<br><br>

## Get a specific article
GET `api.axow.se/site/article?id=<string:article_id>`
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "article": {
        "meta": {
            "id": "<string:article_id>",
            "name": "<string>",
            "author": "<string:profile_id_with_@>",
            "published": <epoch>,
            "last_changed": <epoch>,
            "tags": ["<string>"],
            "group": "<string:group>",
            "category": "<string:category>",
            "favicon": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>",
            "banner": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>"
        },
        "content": "<markdown>"
    }
}
```
<br><br>

## Add/Modify an article
PUT `api.axow.se/site/article?id=<string:article_id>&action=<merge/remove>` (Authed)
```Headers (Request)
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: <string:token>
```
```json (Request)
{
    "meta": {
        "id": "<string:article_id>",
        "name": "<string>",
        "author": "<string:profile_id_with_@>",
        "published": <epoch>,
        "last_changed": <epoch>,
        "tags": ["<string>"],
        "group": "<string:group>",
        "category": "<string:category>",
        "favicon": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>",
        "banner": "<string:optional:url_or_base_url>"
    },
    "content": "<markdown:if-action=merge>"
}
```
(`merge` ensures al meta fields and replaces content, `remove` removes meta fields and does not touch content)
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>"
}
```
<br><br>

## Remove an article
DELETE `api.axow.se/site/article?id=<string:article_id>` (Authed)
```Headers (Request)
Content-Type: application/json
