# Chibit storage
## Get resourcepack repository
GET `api.axow.se/site/chibits/resourcepacks?group_filter=<string:optional>`
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "chibit_repo": {
        "<string:group>": {
            "<string:chibit_uuid>": "<string:chibit_entry_url>"
        }
        ...
    }
}
```
GET `api.axow.se/site/chibits/resourcepacks?group=<string:group>`
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "chibit_repo": {
        "<string:group>": {
            "<string:chibit_uuid>": "<string:chibit_entry_url>"
        }
    }
}
```
GET `api.axow.se/site/chibits/resourcepacks?group=<string:group>&include_entries=true`
```json (Response)
{
    "status": "success"/"failed",
    "msg": "<string:optional>",
    "chibit_repo": {
        "group": "axo77",
        "entries": {
            "<string:chibit_uuid>": {...chibit_entry_data...}
        }
    }
}
```
